<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778344' id='t-778344'>Maybe you're not eating healthy enough.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='780424' id='t-780424'>Eat healthier.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781440' id='t-781440'>It's a pretty simplistic</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='782835' id='t-782835'>approach to root cause analyses.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784241' id='t-784241'>It turns out, it doesn't really work</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='785906' id='t-785906'>when we just limit ourselves that worldview.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='788370' id='t-788370'>The root cause analysis that an upstreamist brings</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='790471' id='t-790471'>to the table is to say, let's look at the living</span>
