<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='795760' id='t-795760'>Perhaps, for children with asthma,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='797842' id='t-797842'>it's what's happening in their home,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799450' id='t-799450'>or perhaps they live close to a
