<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='860760' id='t-860760'>So we decided to start an organization</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='862466' id='t-862466'>called Health Begins,</span>
