<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='885254' id='t-885254'>and working conditions in our lives.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='888261' id='t-888261'>We're seeing nearly a tripling</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='890240' id='t-890240'>of that confidence in our work.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:02
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='891821' id='t-891821'>It's remarkable,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='893124' id='t-893124'>but I'll tell you the most compelling part</span>
