<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:40
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='929489' id='t-929489'>These stories are compelling because</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='931144' id='t-931144'>not only do they tell us that we're this close</span>
