<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='938459' id='t-938459'>Doctors and nurses can get better at asking</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='940321' id='t-940321'>about the context of patients' lives,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='942165' id='t-942165'>not simply because it's better bedside manner,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='944676' id='t-944676'>but frankly, because it's a better standard of care.</span>
